<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>فَكَانَ عُمُوما فِي جَمِيعهم<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>وَالظَّاهِر مثل قَوْله تَعَالَى<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span style="color:#008000">(وءاتوهم من مَال الله الَّذِي آتَاكُم)</span><a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>إِلَّا ظَاهره الْوُجُوب وَيحْتَمل النّدب<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span>وَالْأَمر استدعاء الْفِعْل بالْقَوْل مِمَّن دونه<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>